00:08:54.000 --> 00:08:59.000
And that was another memorable moment.

00:08:59.000 --> 00:09:03.000
Fiona wasn't born at, I don't know, Fiona wasn't around at that time, but I remember thinking this is really great.

00:09:03.000 --> 00:09:06.000
We didn't take to the streets with that, but that was indoor.

00:09:06.000 --> 00:09:08.000
And that was fabulous.

